symptotics of GGF-Fs with large fractional degree $\\nu.$ The second is to\npresent miscellaneous properties of GGF-Fs for better understanding of this\nfamily of useful special functions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Sep 2017 06:18:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 19 Nov 2018 10:46:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-02"}
