s are consistent with recent findings related\nto hydrogen Balmer continuum enhancements, which were clearly detected in disk\nflares by the IRIS near-ultraviolet spectrometer.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Sep 2017 12:45:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-04"}
